summaries.short: Divided between past and future, Genny will have to face his old demons.
summaries.full: Genny travels to London to buy the company responsible for the construction of the airport. But ironically, an unforeseen event will force him to use his old criminal methods to save the clean and legal future he is building with Azzurra. Divided between past and future, Genny will have to face his old demons.

summaries.short: The peace between the clans is in danger when an operation goes wrong and Patrizia will have to show that she has learned to be in charge.
summaries.full: The outdated patriarchal system of the Levantes tests the relationship between Patrizia and Mickey, Gerlando's favorite son. The peace between the clans is in danger when a cocaine operation goes wrong, and to avoid war, Patrizia will have to show that she has learned what it means to be in charge of the most powerful clan in Naples.

summaries.short: A year after Genny left, Patrizia is the head of the clan that supplies cocaine to the rest of the great families of Naples.
summaries.full: A year after Genny left, Patrizia is the head of the clan that supplies cocaine to the rest of the great families of Naples: the Capaccio and the Forcella boys.

summaries.short: After the seizure of the cocaine shipment, Nicola decides to follow the trail of the traitor who has sold them to the police.
summaries.full: After the seizure of the cocaine shipment, Nicola, Patrizia's right-hand man, fears losing his boss' trust and decides to follow the trail of the traitor who has sold them to the police.

summaries.short: Genny discovers that keeping it clean is more difficult than anticipated. And that is impossible to do it without getting your hands dirty.
summaries.full: Genny has become an entrepreneur. His project is to use the profits of cocaine trafficking to build an airport in southern Italy with the help of Alberto Resta, a Neapolitan entrepreneur, to lend his name to the entreprise. But very soon he will discover that keeping it "clean" is more difficult than anticipated. And that is impossible to do it without getting your hands dirty.

summaries.short: The general discontent begins to undermine the leadership of Sangue Blu. The Forcella boys try to find alternative ways to survive.
summaries.full: The general discontent begins to undermine the leadership of Sangue Blu, while the wait for the new cocaine shipment forces the Forcella boys to find alternative ways to survive.

summaries.short: After Ciro's death, Genny's only way of maintaining balance is by bringing a new player to the Neapolitan chessboard: the Levante family.
summaries.full: After Ciro's death, Genny's only way of maintaining balance is by bringing a new player to the Neapolitan chessboard: the Levante family, a clan that controls Naples’ underworld and is infiltrated in every institution. Once the balance of power is restored, Genny will leave everyone unsettled with an unexpected revelation.
